<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA62">
<l>viṇṇakaram veḵkā viritirainīr vēṅkaṭa</l>
<l>maṇṇakara māmāṭa vēḷukkai – maṇṇakatta</l>
<l>teṉkuṭantai tēṉār tiruvaraṅkan teṉkōṭṭi</l>
<l>taṉkuṭaṅkai nīrēṟṟāṉ ṟāḻvu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The heavenly city Veḵkā, Vēṅkaṭam [encircled] by water with expanding waves,</l>
<l>the earth city Vēḷukkai with big mansions, Southern Kuṭantai</l>
<l>interior to(?)  the earth, honey-filled Tiruvaraṅkam, Southern Kōṭṭi</l>
<l>he received humbly, with water in his palm.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
